Group command<br/>
<br/><br/>
Usage split (type)<br/><br/>
<br/><br/>
Used to split money more or less evenly between group members. To split<br/>
loot from a mob while in a group type split &lt;type&gt; Type may be platinum, gold, <br/>
silver, copper or iron. This will split the type of coin indicated as evenly <br/>
as possible between the group members.<br/>  <br/>
